{
  "doc_id": "14290",
  "text": "Furthermore, IDA and environmental analysis have seldom been utilized in an incorporate manner, even though the efficiency analysis method (e.g., SBM) can refine the directions for reductions in CO 2 emission. So far, to the best of knowledge, only Li et al. [CITATION_1] applied IDA and efficiency analysis jointly to derive the driving forces of CO 2 emission and to discover the possibilities for CO 2 emission abatement in the European Union agriculture sector. Methodologically, this paper could be regarded as the first paper to analyze the CO 2 emission from China's electricity generation, specifically China's thermal electricity generation, with the integrated manner containing both the IDA and environmental efficiency methods.",
